###
    NEOVIM TELESCOPE SHORTCUTS
    by luca
###


# OPEN TELESCOPE
<leader><leader>    search recursively files from current folder
<leader>g           grep words in files recursively

# CLOSE TELESCOPE
<C-c>               close telescope window

# TELESCOPE NORMAL MODE
    j | file down
    k | file up
    k | file up

# TELESCOPE INSERT MODE
<C-s>       split selection vertical
<C-h>       split selection horizontal
<C-t>       open selection in new tab

<C-d>       scroll code preview down
<C-u>       scroll code preview up
